headline: Humana (HUM) Is Down 26.8% After Surprise Medicare Advantage Rate Proposal - Has The Bull Case Changed?
summary: Earlier this week, the Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services proposed a roughly flat 0.09% payment increase for 2027 Medicare Advantage plans, far below the 4%–6% range analysts had expected, pressuring insurers like Humana that are highly exposed to this market. At the same time, Humana has been working to enhance care delivery through initiatives such as its partnership with Carda Health to expand at-home cardiac rehabilitation and technology upgrades at CenterWell to streamline...
